data.description: Location, location, location! This beautiful home is located in the desirable Esmond Estates subdivision. It comes with a brand new roof once solar panels are removed prior to closing. This home also features 2 primary bedrooms, with an upstairs game room/flex room or in law suite. Gather around the pool for fun with friends and family and prepare to  enjoy your new fireplace by the holidays! Appliances are staying! What the owner loves: Convenient location and quiet, established neighborhood.
